@node "RICK DANGEROUS"
RICK DANGEROUS

Enter "POOKY" on the high score table and you will continue on the level you
died on.  It is of no use until you can pass level 1.
@endnode
@node "RICK DANGEROUS 2"
RICK DANGEROUS 2

Simply type "Burn in Hell" on the title screen for unlimited lives.
@endnode
@node "RINGS OF MEDUSA"
RINGS OF MEDUSA

After entering your name, type "DESOXYRIBONUKLEINSAEURE", then HELP.  This
will give you a cheat menu.
@endnode
@node "RINGS OF MEDUSA II - RETURN OF MEDUSA"
RINGS OF MEDUSA II - RETURN OF MEDUSA

If you select the selection menu (middle-under) twice, the name "Till Bubeck"
will appear.  Click on the "I" with both mouse buttons while holding down the
'HELP' key.  A cheat menu will appear.
@node "RINGS OF ZON"
RINGS OF ZON

On the game options screen press the 'LEFT AMIGA' key to activate cheat mode,
then in the game use 'F9' and 'F10' to cheat.
@endnode
@node "RISKY WOODS"
RISKY WOODS

While playing:

   Press 'F1' - for more lives
   Press 'F2' - for more money
   Press 'F3' - to skip to next level!
@endnode
@node "ROADBLASTERS"
ROADBLASTERS

