09 Level 6-3               27 Level 7-3          45 Bonus Level 15
10 Level 1 and 2 Boss      28 Lewel 7-4          46 Bonus Level 16
11 Level 5 and 6 Boss      29 Level 7-5          47 Bonus Level 17
12 Level 7 and 8 Boss      30 Level 5-1          48 Hard Level 
