@node "ROTOR"
ROTOR

Here are some codes for higher levels:

Level 1 - "GAG"
      2 - "LIP"
      3 - "FLY"
      4 - "MEN"
      5 - "AWE"
      6 - "TNT"

Also, "PIT" allows access to the battle simulator.
@endnode
@node "ROTOX"
ROTOX

At any time, type: "AARDVARK" and hit 'RETURN' for infinite credits.
@endnode        
@node "RUBICON"
RUBICON

To activate a number of cheats, pause the game by pressing the 'Space Bar'
and type "THE REAPER".  This will automatically activate the infinite lives
cheat and give you the ability to select your favorite weapon by using the
keys 'F1' to 'F7'.  To recharge your weapons, press the 'F10' key.  To skip
levels, pause the game and press the 'L' key.
@endnode
@node "RUNNING MAN"
RUNNING MAN

Get onto the high score table and enter your name as 'DdIiSsKk' (that`s the
word Disk in UPPER and lower case text, merged together).  This should give
you infinite energy.
@endnode

        
